## what is the [hacker](http://www.catb.org/esr/faqs/hacker-howto.html#what_is) [hive](https://www.hackerhive.net)?

the [hacker hive](https://www.hackerhive.net) is an initiative in the spirit of existing [hacker](http://www.catb.org/esr/faqs/hacker-howto.html#what_is) [communities](http://hackerspaces.org/) to create cooperative living spaces that subsidise living expenses through collective creative [[output]].

if this idea appeals to you, please participate and get all your friends who you wish to live with to also participate.

there is no chain of command. nothing will get done until someone decides to do it, so start doing!

